Documentation for clsharedir:

Sharedir is a little program to share directory with other host.

After installing (see INSTALL), start clsharedir as server part
in the directory you want to share:

$ your-lisp load.lisp --server

and then others can see your directory vith a web browser (at
http://your_adresse:clsharedir_port).

They also can download/upload file to your directory with the
client part of clsharedir.

$ your-lisp load.lisp --content   =>  query content from a directory
                                      server
$ your-lisp load.lisp --copy      =>  copy content from server
                                      directory in localhost directory
$ your-lisp load.lisp --save      =>  save content from localhost
                                      directory to server directory



